{"tid":155135,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺80後係生不逢時？","createTime":"2017-03-13T19:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T14:42:21.000Z","uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d79d15cbfd9af87a5d58babe55895a9cc8d9f9","tid":155135,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T19:40:26.000Z","msg":"眼見90後之中90-93年嗰班好似好多都早婚，但80後30歲-37歲嗰班好多都未婚，諗諗下可能係咁：<br />\n<br />\n80年嗰班人一17歲出嚟社會就撞正97金融風暴同基建潮完結（第一次civil爆煲）。<br />\n<br />\n上到大學讀it嗰班，三年後就到2000科網股爆破。<br />\n<br />\n再三年後，SARS 全民仆街，hku 出黎有$4000一個月都要還神。<br />\n<br />\n之後幾年都好返啲，但08年又一個金融海潚殺到。<br />\n<br />\n仕途上每幾年就有人禍殺出，搞到30歲前經常經歷減薪裁員潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係想話嚟個鬥仆街的魚蛋論，90後會否到現時經歷過的大風浪少啲，所以可以早啲成婚？"},{"pid":"f1c43e49ba4484f8acdb35a515e0ec5d4abc6ead","tid":155135,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T19:51:10.000Z","msg":"幾有道理 <br />\n但點解拉埋結婚黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d35f746f3b7796718b58ba48d9555865bbc25e1","tid":155135,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T20:37:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4370502c9127275b49ca69c8eb6942d61ca4909b","tid":155135,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾有道理 <br />\n但點解拉埋結婚黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為後生果陣一直都面對裁員減薪潮，到開始穩定、有積蓄果陣，男男女女都過哂30歲<br />\n<br />\n90後果班我都想知點解佢地咁快有錢結婚，定全部靠父幹"},{"pid":"c3a69d89744e69e58b7f4e587f95ab7b9e808d70","tid":155135,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:16:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/117847/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/117847/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fe701f5512b455e08a5e9ebdfea7b99385c270a6","tid":155135,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:11:01.000Z","ms